      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AMELIAS JEWEL (4) is at the track for the first time. By champion sire Bettors Delight from a multiple Group 1 placed mare and hails from the powerhouse Emma Stewart stable. Runner-up in her latest trial here and is sure to be well educated. Can kick off with a win. PET WOLF (1) has placed in his two starts at this circuit so far. Came from the back row to miss by a neck on debut then broke but recovered for third last time. Has had eight weeks off since but has upside and gets the ace draw. STEEL MIKI (6) is looming as a threat after a good effort last start, coming from the back row and missing by just a nose when second at Bendigo. LIBERTY STAR DUST (5) showed good improvement to finish third in his second outing at Bendigo last time. Could progress further.",
